msgid "NODATA"
msgstr "NODATA"

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:69
msgid "域名系统工作原理"
msgstr "How the Domain Name System Works"

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:72
msgid "解析过程"
msgstr "Resolution Process"

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:73
msgid "DNS解析过程是递归查询的，具体过程如下："
msgstr "DNS resolution is a recursive query process. The detailed flow is as follows:"

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:75
msgid "用户要访问域名www.example.com时，先查看本机hosts是否有记录或者本机是否有DNS缓存，如果有，直接返回结果，否则向递归服务器查询该域名的IP地址"
msgstr ""
"When a user wants to access the domain name www.example.com, the local hosts "
"file and local DNS cache are checked first. If a record exists, the result is "
"returned directly; otherwise, the client asks a recursive server for the IP "
"address of the domain name."

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:76
msgid "递归缓存为空时，首先向根服务器查询com顶级域的IP地址"
msgstr ""
"If the recursive cache is empty, the recursive server first queries a root "
"server for the IP address of the ``com`` top-level domain."

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:77
msgid "根服务器告知递归服务器com顶级域名服务器的IP地址"
msgstr ""
"The root server tells the recursive server the IP address of the ``com`` "
"top-level domain name server."

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:78
msgid "递归向com顶级域名服务器查询负责example.com的权威服务器的IP"
msgstr ""
"The recursive server queries the ``com`` top-level domain name server for "
"the IP address of the authoritative server responsible for example.com."

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:79
msgid "com顶级域名服务器返回相应的IP地址"
msgstr "The ``com`` top-level domain name server returns the corresponding IP address."

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:80
msgid "递归向example.com的权威服务器查询www.example.com的地址记录"
msgstr ""
"The recursive server queries the authoritative server for example.com for "
"the address record of www.example.com."

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:81
msgid "权威服务器告知www.example.com的地址记录"
msgstr "The authoritative server returns the address record for www.example.com."

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:82
msgid "递归服务器将查询结果返回客户端"
msgstr "The recursive server returns the query result to the client."

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:85
msgid "域传送"
msgstr "Zone Transfer"

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:86
msgid "DNS服务器可以分为主服务器、备份服务器和缓存服务器。域传送是指备份服务器从主服务器拷贝数据，并使用得到的数据更新自身数据库。域传送是在主备服务器之间同步数据库的机制。"
msgstr ""
"DNS servers can be divided into primary servers, secondary servers, and "
"caching servers. A zone transfer is the process in which a secondary server "
"copies data from a primary server and uses the data to update its own "
"database. It is the mechanism used to synchronize the database between "
"primary and secondary servers."

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:89
msgid "服务器类型"
msgstr "Server Types"

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:92
msgid "根服务器"
msgstr "Root Server"

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:93
msgid "根服务器是DNS的核心，负责互联网顶级域名的解析，用于维护域的权威信息，并将DNS查询引导到相应的域名服务器。"
msgstr ""
"Root servers are the core of DNS. They are responsible for resolving "
"Internet top-level domains, maintaining authoritative information for the "
"root zone, and directing DNS queries to the appropriate name servers."

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:95
msgid "根服务器在域名树中代表最顶级的 ``.`` 域， 一般省略。"
msgstr ""
"In the domain name tree, root servers represent the top-level ``.`` domain, "
"which is usually omitted."

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:97
msgid ""
"13台IPv4根服务器的域名标号为a到m，即a.root-servers.org到m.root-"
"servers.org，所有服务器存储的数据相同，仅包含ICANN批准的TLD域名权威信息。"
msgstr ""
"The 13 IPv4 root servers are labeled from a to m, namely a.root-servers.org "
"through m.root-servers.org. All of these servers store the same data, which "
"contains only authoritative information for TLDs approved by ICANN."

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:100
msgid "权威服务器"
msgstr "Authoritative Server"

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:101
msgid "权威服务器上存储域名Zone文件，维护域内域名的权威信息，递归服务器可以从权威服务器获得DNS查询的资源记录。"
msgstr ""
"Authoritative servers store domain zone files and maintain authoritative "
"information for names within the domain. Recursive servers can obtain DNS "
"resource records from authoritative servers."

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:103
msgid "权威服务器需要在所承载的域名所属的TLD管理局注册，同一个权威服务器可以承载不同TLD域名，同一个域也可以有多个权威服务器。"
msgstr ""
"An authoritative server must be registered with the TLD registry for the "
"domain names it hosts. The same authoritative server can host domain names "
"under different TLDs, and a single domain can also have multiple "
"authoritative servers."

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:106
msgid "递归服务器"
msgstr "Recursive Server"

#: ../../source/network/domain/basic.rst:107
msgid "递归服务器负责接收用户的查询请求，进行递归查询并响应用户查询请求。在初始时递归服务器仅有记录了根域名的Hint文件。"
msgstr ""
"Recursive servers receive user queries, perform recursive lookups, and "
"respond to the user's requests. Initially, a recursive server only has a hint "
"file that records the root domain names."
